            <title>[FELIX-5136] Felix Fileinstall temp dir generation is inefficient</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-5136</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If no tmpDir is set, DirectoryWatcher will use a SecureRandom to find a free temp dir.&lt;br/&gt;
This is ineffcient, because SecureRandom needs warmup time.&lt;br/&gt;
Additionally DirectoryWatcher wil unncessarily hold on to java.io.tmpdir and the secure random after intitialization.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
